The paper deals with deep learning models for face recognition, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) category. The paper also discusses model compression techniques, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper evaluates the performance of the proposed approach on datasets, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses the hardware-friendly nature of the proposed approach, which is related to computer security and cryptography (cs.CR) sub-category.
